description: JSON Response Rules
alwaysApply: true
---

# JSON Responses

- Always use this envelope format:
  Success: { data: {}, meta: { page:, per_page:, total: } }
  Error: { errors: [{ field:, message: }] }
- Use jbuilder or explicit as_json — do NOT use ActiveModel::Serializers
- Never expose: password_digest, internal IDs in unexpected places, 
  raw error messages, stack traces